{"tid":96941,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新年送禮大行動！！","createTime":"2017-01-27T09:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T18:10:09.000Z","uid":11614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db96a7069ebebaad863671a649da923b7f46744c","tid":96941,"uid":11614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"各位熱愛足球嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下3件AC Milan嘅波衫係小弟嘅珍藏（唔係咩落場辦貴野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但由於我保養不善<br />\n令到每件衫都帶有瑕疵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （熨No.的膠字甩色）<br />\n<br />\n再者波衫始終都應該係綠茵場上奔馳<br />\n所以現在免費送俾有需要的巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3件均為細碼（最後一件長袖背後係熨字）<br />\n係天水圍交收<br />\nTG：TG_Vincent<br />\n<br />\n每人只限一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLr78O9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLr78O9.jpg&h=6583dfb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/27/170921_a3763abaa8458dae782196e16b3d66db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F27%2F170921_a3763abaa8458dae782196e16b3d66db.jpg&h=c929a9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h790oiE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh790oiE.jpg&h=808b2db2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/690odJy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u